Package com.github.nradov.abnffuzzer.antlr4

Interface AbnfListener

All Superinterfaces:
ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbnfBaseListener
public interface AbnfListener
extends ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by AbnfParser.
